<div class="tag">{{type}}</div>
<h2>Hello {{userName}},</h2>
<p>The status of your order on <strong>bulkmandi</strong> has been updated.</p>

<div style="padding: 20px; background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1e293b;">Order ID: {{orderId}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #64748b;">New Status: <span style="font-weight: bold; color: #2563eb;">{{status}}</span></p>
</div>

<p>You can view the full details of this order in your dashboard, including any attached documents.</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{orderUrl}}" class="btn">View Order Details</a>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px;">Thank you for using bulkmandi for your transactions.</p>
